title: KOLCHAK THE NIGHT STALKER 03 They Have Been.They Are.They Will B
description:
KOLCHAK THE NIGHT STALKER (1974)

3. They Have Been, They Are, They Will Be...   9/27/1974 
A bizarre force sweeps through Chicago, killing randomly. It has the strength of a hurricane, generates a massive electromagnetic field, steals lead and electronic equipment, and sucks the bone marrow out of humans and animals. Carl realizes he&#039;s onto a huge story - if he can find out exactly what this force is.


This was originally released on Demonoid and has been circulating sporadically via DHT. 
I thought it would be good to try to join the swarms together and give it new life. 
I&#039;m sure Kolchak would approve. ;)
